breastrad

Entry Element BreastRadiologyReport

Documentation:

Breast Radiology Diagnostic Report. <br>This diagnostic report is the base of the Breast Radiology Report, and contains a summary of the report findings. <br>Detailed information about the reports document is contained in the Breast Radiology Document linked to by the [resultComposition] field.
